      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uhdenß-Pluhdu (fuhtiht)/ taē\nKUNGS fehsch par Rehmizu labbu Prahtu effi tu man\nmuhſchigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS dohs fa-\nweem Landim Stiprumu / tad es iſtruhzinajohs.\nwĩsch ſwehtihś tawus Landis\nar Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXX. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Pateifschanas-Dseefma / eekſch ka\nwiſch pateiz/ ka Deewß winnu no ta Wella\nleelahm Rahrdinaschanahm atyeftiis: 2/ etc.\nEeprezina arridsan/ ka Deews tikai wee-\nnu Azzumirſcli duhno / un winnam muhfu\nBehdas un Nahwe ne patihkus: 6/ etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "W Eena Dseefma no Dah-\nwida Namna Eeſiweh-\ntifchanas dseedama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es tevi augsti teikſchu\nKUNGS/ jo tu effi mann aug-\nsti uszehlis/ un mannus Eenaid-\nneekus pahr mannim ne eepee-\nzeis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS/ mans Deews/\nkad es tevis peefanzu/ tad tu\nmann dseedinaji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS/ tu effi mann\nDwehfeli no Elles iſweddıs/ tu\neffı man dſihwu usturrejs / ka\nes ne etmu Elłe nogrinunis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dseedajt tam KUNGant\njuhs winna Swehtee/ un teizect\npar winna Swehtibas Peemin-\nnefchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo winna Duymiba pa-\nleek Azzumirſcli/ ta Osihwofcha-\nna winnam gribbahs / Watkarā\npaleek zaar Naſti ta Rauda-\nſchanu/ bet Rihta irr Preeks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gann es fazziju eekſch\nmannas Labkahfchanas / es\nmuhſchan ne fchaubifchohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo KURGS / zaur ta-\nKalnu pastahwign darrijs /\nkad tu tawu Waigu patleh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tewis veetauzu es KUNG\nun peeluhdsu tew ak KUNG\nno Sirđs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kahds Labbuns atte\nno mannahım Affinim / kad\nKappā buhſchu grimmis/ arr-\ntee Pihſchli tew pateiks ? w-\ntee tawn Bateefibu paſludd-\nnahs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaufi KUNGS / un a-\nschehlojees pahr mannim\nKUNGS/ effiman par Paligu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu effi mannı Schehla-\nschanu par Lihgfmetchanu pahr-\nwehrtis/ tu effi man to Mais-\niswilzis/ un mann ar Preek-\napjohsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz dseedahs ten-\nmans Gohds/ un kluſtu ne zee-\ntihs/ KUNGS mans Deews/\nes pateikſchu tew muhſchigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXXI. Dseefma.\nWeena Lugſchana Kristus/ ka winna Debbeſ-\nTeḥws eekſch winna Zeeschanas un Mir-\nſchanas / kas winnam preekſcha stahw/ n-\ngribbetu likt Kauna tapt: 2/ etc. Ar t-\nEeprezinaſchanu / zaur fo wiſch Jawā-\nBehdas atspirdinajeis: 15. etc\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "W Eena Dahwida Dseef-\nma/ preekſch ta augsta-\nDseedataja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Us tevi KUNGS/ es pa-\ntaujoſs/ ne leež manni Kannā-\ntapt muhſchigi/ iſglahb mann-\nzaur tawu Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atgreeſ tawu Auſi pee-\nman-\n"
    }
  ],
